<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFKohlberg1973">Kohlberg, Lawrence (1973). "The Claim to Moral Adequacy of a Highest Stage of Moral Judgment". <i>Journal of Philosophy</i> <b>70</b>: 630–646. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2025030" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2025030" rel="nofollow">10.2307/2025030</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+Claim+to+Moral+Adequacy+of+a+Highest+Stage+of+Moral+Judgment&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Philosophy&amp;rft.aulast=Kohlberg&amp;rft.aufirst=Lawrence&amp;rft.au=Kohlberg%2C+Lawrence&amp;rft.date=1973&amp;rft.volume=70&amp;rft.pages=630%E2%80%93646&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.2307%2F2025030&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Kohlberg%27s_stages_of_moral_development"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFKohlberg1981">Kohlberg, Lawrence (1981). <i>Essays on Moral Development, Vol. I: The Philosophy of Moral Development</i>. San Francisco, CA: Harper &amp; Row. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0060647604" class="internal">ISBN 0-06-064760-4</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Essays+on+Moral+Development%2C+Vol.+I%3A+The+Philosophy+of+Moral+Development&amp;rft.aulast=Kohlberg&amp;rft.aufirst=Lawrence&amp;rft.au=Kohlberg%2C+Lawrence&amp;rft.date=1981&amp;rft.place=San+Francisco%2C+CA&amp;rft.pub=Harper+%26+Row&amp;rft.isbn=0-06-064760-4&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Kohlberg%27s_stages_of_moral_development"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
